Hello?

102
00:06:12,973 --> 00:06:16,068
Jingle Bells. Number One Elf speaking.

103
00:06:16,443 --> 00:06:18,104
And Jangle Bells.

104
00:06:18,445 --> 00:06:20,174
Will you stop that?

105
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,571
May I ask who is calling, please?

106
00:06:23,350 --> 00:06:26,877
Hi, Mrs. Claus! Yes, Mrs. Claus.

107
00:06:27,254 --> 00:06:28,688
Okay, Mrs. Claus.

108
00:06:28,755 --> 00:06:31,986
Sure thing, Mrs. Claus.
Right away, Mrs. Claus.

109
00:06:32,592 --> 00:06:33,821
Who was that?

110
00:06:33,894 --> 00:06:34,918
That was...

111
00:06:35,295 --> 00:06:36,592
Come on.

112
00:06:39,499 --> 00:06:42,434
It fits. It fits very nicely.

113
