00:14:25,298 --> 00:14:28,700
Riding a Vixen the wrong way
on a one-way street...

247
00:14:28,835 --> 00:14:30,428
...crossing the white line...

248
00:14:30,636 --> 00:14:33,799
...and wearing funny-looking suits
on a Sunday.

249
00:14:33,873 --> 00:14:34,738
But--

250
00:14:34,874 --> 00:14:36,672
Tell it to the judge.

251
00:14:36,876 --> 00:14:39,504
Maybe they don't like reindeer
in these parts.

252
00:14:39,946 --> 00:14:43,348
