to be very upset about it.

297
00:17:06,659 --> 00:17:08,753
Upset? Why should I be upset?

298
00:17:08,861 --> 00:17:10,260
Yeah, what's the big deal?

299
00:17:10,363 --> 00:17:13,094
You mean, you don't care
if Santa Claus comes or not?

300
00:17:13,366 --> 00:17:14,390
None of you?

301
00:17:14,467 --> 00:17:15,957
No.

302
00:17:16,369 --> 00:17:18,736
Of course not. It's none of our business.

303
00:17:18,804 --> 00:17:22,240
Besides, believing in Santa Claus
is for little kids.

304
00:17:22,308 --> 00:17:23,469
Yeah.

305
00:17:23,609 --> 00:17:25,008
This is serious.

306
00:17:25,077 --> 00:17:26,909
It's worse than I thought.

307
00:17:27,280 --> 00:17:31,478
