I certainly did.

398
00:23:46,625 --> 00:23:49,686
I thought there was something different
about that man.

399
00:23:50,229 --> 00:23:53,221
Mr. Claus. He must be...

400
00:23:53,432 --> 00:23:57,027
Wouldn't surprise me a bit.
At the moment, nothing would.

401
00:23:57,803 --> 00:24:01,103
Then his friends must be real elves
and their dog...

402
00:24:01,941 --> 00:24:04,171
I'll bet that dog was a baby reindeer.

403
00:24:04,777 --> 00:24:08,577
That's bad. They won't know how
to take care of a reindeer at the dog pound.

404
00:24:08,647 --> 00:24:11,241
I wish there was something I could do.

405
00:24:11,317 --> 00:24:15,254
When you've got a big problem, Son,
it often pays to go right to the top man.

406
00:24:15,788 --> 00:24:19,349
Why don't you stop by the mayor's office?
Tell him the whole story.

407
00:24:20,059 --> 00:24:21,458
He should be able to help.

408
00:24:21,527 --> 00:24:23,291
Good idea, Dad.

409
00:24:24,163 --> 00:24:28,293
<i>Well, it just so happened that Jingle
and Jangle had the same good idea...</i>

410
00:24:28,767 --> 00:24:32,135
