to the mayor.</i>

412
00:24:39,545 --> 00:24:42,810
Now, let me see if I got this straight.

413
00:24:44,984 --> 00:24:47,544
You two are elves...

414
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:50,451
...and that dog down at the pound...

415
00:24:50,756 --> 00:24:52,417
...is a reindeer...

416
00:24:53,292 --> 00:24:56,557
...and you want to take him back
to Santa Claus.

417
00:24:57,162 --> 00:24:58,493
At the North Pole.

418
00:25:02,401 --> 00:25:05,598
You see, your honor,
we're here on a special mission.

419
00:25:06,105 --> 00:25:07,231
A secret mission.

420
00:25:08,340 --> 00:25:10,502
A secret mission. I should have guessed.

421
00:25:10,743 --> 00:25:13,212
'Cause Santa isn't coming this year.

422
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:16,073
He wants to take a holiday.

423
00:25:19,918 --> 00:25:22,615
No more, please. I can't take any more.

424
00:25:22,988 --> 00:25:26,356
Reindeer, Santa Claus, elves.

425
00:25:27,259 --> 00:25:29,694
But, we are elves. We're serious.

426
00:25:30,362 --> 00:25:32,194
How can we convince you?

427
00:25:32,898 --> 00:25:35,868
Come on, son.
What kind of fool do you think I am?

428
00:25:36,135 --> 00:25:40,697
