435
00:26:00,225 --> 00:26:04,492
You conjure up a good old-fashioned
white Christmas for us...

436
00:26:04,663 --> 00:26:06,427
...right here in Southtown...

437
00:26:06,498 --> 00:26:08,796
...and I'll buy every word you say.

438
00:26:08,867 --> 00:26:10,028
You will?

439
00:26:10,102 --> 00:26:13,766
I'll spring your reindeer
from the hoosegow.

440
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:17,967
I'll call all the mayors in the U.S. of A.

441
00:26:18,277 --> 00:26:22,805
We'll give Santa
an official national holiday this year.

442
00:26:26,085 --> 00:26:27,416
It's a deal.

443
00:26:29,588 --> 00:26:32,285
Good-bye, your honor.
We've got lots to do.

444
00:26:32,357 --> 00:26:35,554
