asking about her...

466
00:28:03,682 --> 00:28:05,172
Two funny little characters.

467
00:28:05,250 --> 00:28:08,515
They were here about an hour ago,
but they couldn't pay the fine.

468
00:28:08,587 --> 00:28:10,521
I told them to go see the mayor.

469
00:28:11,557 --> 00:28:14,424
What am I gonna do about those two?

470
00:28:15,594 --> 00:28:17,585
Don't you worry, Vixen.

471
00:28:18,597 --> 00:28:21,066
